messageBody:
This is a note to the other moderators of this list. I am not looking
for new moderators (yet).

I need help moderating this group. Right now, messages could go three or
four days without being approved. We need at least one more active approver.

Thanks.
--
J. B. (Joe) Rainsberger
Diaspar Software Services
http://www.diasparsoftware.com
Author, JUnit Recipes: Practical Methods for Programmer Testing
